# Wrangler static assets: only RELATIVE URLs allowed.
# www -> apex: use Cloudflare Dashboard -> Rules -> Redirect Rules (see seo/cloudflare-setup.md).
#
# No rules currently needed: html_handling is "none" (wrangler.jsonc), and
# worker.js explicitly serves index.html for directory-style requests
# (including root /). A prior "/index.html -> /" rule here caused a redirect
# loop against that worker logic (ASSETS.fetch() applies _redirects even to
# requests constructed internally by the worker) — removed; index.html's own
# <link rel="canonical" href="https://seowithfaiz.com/"> already handles SEO
# consolidation without a hard redirect.
